ALL OF THOSE CONDITIONS MUST BE MET BEFORE THE FOLLOWING APPLIES:    In these circumstances...  
|n^|5|at|
        if the bidding is at the 6-level  2ND-IN-HAND: PASSES  with  1st round  control of their suit 
|n^|2|at|^r OR DOUBLES with no such Control.
|n#|2|at|OR   if the bidding is at the 5-level 2ND-IN-HAND: PASSES  with  1st^*b or ^*n2nd  round control
|n^|2|at|^r OR DOUBLES with no such Control.
|n^|5|at|
See my comments on (4) above to clarify what I mean here 
|n#|2|at|    ^c4TH-IN-HAND:  DOUBLES   or  BIDS ON  depending on their holding, in the light of partner's action
^t	and the bidding thus far.|
